Installations : 

1. sudo apt update
2. dnf update -y (RHL 8)
3. apt install ansible 


Installation of Ansible on GCP - RHL8. 

 1000  dnf update -y
 1001  apt install ansible
 1002  sudo dnf install https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-8.noarch.rpm
 1003  sudo dnf install ansible
 1004  ansible --version
 1005  sudo dnf install ansible
 1006  ansible -version
 1007  ansible --version
 1008  history
